Getting Started
Branchy_VGG:
Download Cifar-10 dataset and locate it in './data/cifar-10-python/cifar-10-batches-py' folder
python --phase train
python --phase test
You can set hyperparameters such as epochs and learning rate by adding arguments (check main function in solver.py)
The model structure is located in VGG.py

VggNet_Cifar_10_RL
Download Cifar-10 dataset and locate it in './data/cifar-10-python/cifar-10-batches-py' folder
for server:
python environment.py
for client:
python MODEL/Client/solver.py
IP settings can be found in solver.py (for both server and client)

For more information, contact Zhihe Zhao via zz208@duke.edu
